    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Depictions, often sculptural, of the crucified Christ on Golgotha in the midst of crucified criminals and those present, including Mary, his mother, apostle John, Mary Magdalene, Roman soldiers etc.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
